<div id="accordion" class="accordion">

    <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
                <span class="title">What is LLF?</span>
                <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
          	<p>LIVING X LIFE X FEARLESS (LLF) is a brand dedicated to creativity and culture, and that can cover a lot of different areas. Whether that's through the arts, music, fashion, extreme sports, branding or others, we strive to celebrate all forms and aim to shine a light on those individuals and brands doing amazing things for the culture.</p>

            <p>You can follow everything we're up to as a brand on our official profile: <%= link_to "llfofficial", :controller => "search", :action => "search", :discover => "llfofficial" %></p>
          </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
                <span class="title">What is this website?</span>
                <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
            <p>This website is a growing community for creative individuals and brands to connect with other creatives, create and share amazing content, and discover incredible content.</p>

            <p>We provide a great platform for our members to share their media, events, projects, and listings. While in turn discovering great content from other like-minded creative individuals and brands.</p>

            <p>In short, a place to inspire and be inspired.</p>
          </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
                <span class="title">Is it free?</span>
                <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
          	<p>YES! It is free to use and always will be.</p>
          </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
                <span class="title">Why should I join the community?</span>
                <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
          	<p>We give you the platform to show exactly who you are and what you're all about; whether that's through your artwork, photos, poems, podcasts, songs, beats, events, projects, products, or services, we've got you covered.</p>

          	<p>We've also got the community to back you up. You'll find some of the most creative, amazing, and inspiring people and brands that you'll be able to connect and interact with on a real level.</p>

            <p>Surrounding yourself with other great creative minds can only benefit your own work.</p>
          </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
                <span class="title">How do I get started?</span>
                <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content ordered">
          	<ul>
          		<li>
          			<strong>Join the Community</strong> To get started click 'Join!' in the top menu and fill out the short form to get to your profile. It only takes 30 seconds.
          		</li>
          		<li>
          			<strong>Fill Out Your Profile</strong> We suggest uploading an avatar, listing your pursuits (interests), and a couple of your social networks for a strong start. 
          		</li>
          		<li>
          			<strong>Find Someone to Follow</strong> Browse the stream on your profile page or go to the discover page (compass icon) and start browsing or searching by your favorite pursuits and follow some others. 
          		</li>
          		<li>
          			<strong>Start Creating</strong> Now that your stream is flowing a little (pun intended), start creating some content of your own. Post your first status and upload some media. 
          		</li>
          		<li>
          			<strong>Explore</strong> Now you're ready to get out there and start exploring the various pages. The stream is a great place to get inspired.
          		</li>
          	</ul>
          </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
                <span class="title">How do I edit my profile?</span>
                <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
          	<p>You can edit your profile by clicking the account settings link on your profile (the gear icon) or by clicking on your image in the top menu and going to account settings. </p>
          </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
                <span class="title">What are pursuits?</span>
                <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
          	<p>Pursuits are the things that you love to do. They are your favorite interests and passions in life. For example, branding, graphic design, music prodiction, etc. They are also the primary way in which people/brands can connect. </p>
          </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
                <span class="title">Why am I not receiving any notifications?</span>
                <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
                <p>We notify you by email when another user starts a new conversation with you, leaves a comment on one of your posts, follows you, or mentions you.</p>

                <p>If you're not receiving these emails, please check your email clients' spam folder. Adding noreply@livinglifefearless.co to your contacts will ensure that you receive all future emails.</p>
          </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
                <span class="title">How do I close my account?</span>
                <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
          	<p>If you wish to close your account you must go to your settings, go to the 'Account Settings' tab, and there is a button at the bottom that reads 'Leave the Community'.</p>

          	<p>Keep in mind that <strong>this can not be undone</strong> and you will lose all of your data.</p>
          </div>
    </div>
    <div class="accordion-item">
          <div class="accordion-header">
                <span class="title">Tips & Tricks</span>
                <i class="fa fa-plus"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="accordion-content">
          	<ul>
          		<li>
          			Include specific pursuits (i.e. indie folk) to increase your chances of connecting with the right people.
          		</li>
          		<li>
          			You can create multiple accounts, one for you and one for your brand.
          		</li>
          		<li>
          			Favorite posts to bookmark them on your profile.
          		</li>
          		<li>
          			Think before you post! There are no privacy controls.
          		</li>
          		<li>
          			Subscribe to our blog for updates about the community and LLF: <a href="http://beboldbefearlss.co" target="_blank">http://beboldbefearless.co</a>
          		</li>
          		<li>
          			For more general support questions, concerns, or suggestions; <%= link_to "Contact Us", "#contact", :data => {:toggle => "modal"} %>.
          		</li>
          	</ul>
          </div>
    </div>

</div>